[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Exploring Java MMap functionality**\n\nI’m looking into why the javap command only shows MMap output, especially since grep for \"Ram\" returns no matches. I think the --add-opens option might be necessary due to MMap unmap. With Java 25, I wonder if it will degrade but not fail without add-opens. The native image might require an agent, and I suspect the docs mention MMapDirectory may use undocumented APIs. I’ll look for Javadocs related to MMapDirectory and its \"UNMAP_SUPPORTED\" status, ensuring no extra setup is needed.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_06bec2678c5d726f016a3fa20bfe20819388935512a2870b68\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqP6IPQC_N3BZ8zqfrymrJiWqC0iqJY0Q7eePoXEcC0ktf7WdXihOC9yMtJeCzTtc48JC8UB-cpbchxd8dI1W7E4is2ZvPJLg9RmNWYECW3fM11VQvCQKy_oneNRwsQnDG_bBiGthyg8IAfFEqW9nPu9sy0XL2kOdox287pfG2TOTLob4Q4TMo0paoWeFa1OfKWLp-AvG7-NWpd2A07g4FIeGLtX7rwAZsDBExcgnhWnjrTi0jQuYwVZAYWB_erEi3sWFpIJY9j9eo33FMs6QNPBJfFDj6N47mRusX1gbEo5axBcvvYnms_p80tUuhmE-95UcuX00OCtq7ncYuKTSHQPK0jfVlTar5dJxwZ8k69RH-NzlSaNl6DRQrHOU-obw5MW_nOhhweajIGMgCF1TT8JMhe21VOZfhO6C-Vlb2ZXaUvdliCK8lFI4g45f1MD3fCAMfWow2UwENBtzI5rm2KfZ3HZV4wbPrNrC3KstvlWEOlexRlTMKZsuAbNT-Umys1ClC3c8vR8ees__ia6qEgMdbm_GIa16yz0F24GHrjPMTHIIGpACZBb3sQ-PUDNVgGgbvJu7xWydADspwrr_ac85mQsffMZe9a_mFS01kTdmvJQrZ_FQ0_l956ctslbPiUIb22YL_jVjjZPWiu8oINWkxSQm2Ir0lOJZXu45Zytgs3ocbULB9DukJNKGLaG7mnkjRtMRqb9DlbwQD5gok1nKkB2ia55QzUf4Z9Lu6mruH6XYP4H-YOuhXsqisFucz8WOkNoEXnf3IWjhySUf807k3U30Ho1EY1HyStY7FuQBdf-UsGBDDhtkYLphtuLQIqVLe_8e6nDwlpN5cwEp0UYqWT9CGCY-1WYqDYaSwxglCODqHWaEkFE8SbgnKwsrakehSiV7WbdNkbxLme5UhPh_J2R-XS9ytilIvh7Tm_Z9CNO2-nubdmhLfEFe_SHvx3bmrFp1UrTPwfVV6lAgUE1NtrVBwmoXqkuoHGGynphWi8KdPqWlIiBW31P5pjVWpRN74WTfeHodWH0oUR0TbfEinmXO0EfARJ_uhAx6BdsN46y4oPNyTGL8j-YvVdgl-_p-9Ok88mGhmXJS-Yga61QzN4vTjjwC3wBHAYK_GMhDwKviwqF9NulViQ4wXmUJX6GHeNzMJn50f1aMTkSP3RFWByNw0Pxp0GuPyxoRdrGGw3Wmp