[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Exploring workflow processes**\n\nI'm thinking about how a Forge workflow might create a worktree, set a new version, run a compile that could fail, and then ask an agent to fix things. This preflight decision likely sets up a deterministic preparation before generating anything, like adding dependencies or Docker. If there's a compile failure, I don't need any extra setup. The agent fixing the compile should be aware of how `AttributeImpl` reflects, and the usual generated scaffold already contains a `build.gradle`.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_06bec2678c5d726f016a3fa21f81948193ae727d01b4db48b0\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqP6IoxaIYCcrDCEeS8eOHNBHIMh11hAoihtKfWeud2tlxpY1qQBl6Mh5AG6pMkjUP7LYAYll-0xSSkLh4j62BDP6JcI0idL8bPNiDcaCqpGZd3nMDQKWV_BrIjLFwb8u-5NQvXhYd0ZbEEITSZ-2asZjcUaYooRR4iKZqp0H_ieW2IRHAosL58QZMvPyFo1uUyAr2Bm3CpaeFS8KTWy_JaWNzJ4BLpppajKLyvCpcs7oRQzr2BccTiFXaaBsPqkD0AMN3pJDIHCH8HcMmOet0AGcSk596tTqwAMDc7AFxhAtSZ7YZfu9u6oi4sHyzMy3patOZ9FTR2hPeZYPzN6H9nGFZhzGkNVGGzFxaGPFJmTm0K6swR3_whGazvIu5j7EoDHKgbJgewFOXgrOuEgBXTOHJq8iBp0UV8OTd_0QeWSoUrr3A30yIqszT4POYMT3hfUGqOcvdAkWXD1bYScb8cMqhTbfj879ESTjM95B_WwZLW05BbdfAlxmz-EE0K8o5mOOkygtv6UmCdqPtFBm6C3IlxOO5ws00NPnDdo2HngR8Q39fMo-oq4a3xamzF_KmOMRu784CL6fki7uPFpnSush67lIUtiSVik269QhhW59z8oIF8_CxzTlInztAF2JJsJNLvH5dC0clnPd2i4JIm7s-JZIjooVDy5ORTcK9x3S4DiGsiwzf726IeAtGyjKXxsXGepVPQbbuwy7b8Vb8KUBi5WqP2F4qdb5qm_rjYRHprIiYhgL1hB0ULSgJkAY-s14eZz7JfDKT9GREbxmFJ920s1Oe6SOk1YsNMznCZ_fuEElAOlvBoos9rcCv58xoCrT9-4WbkH3S8Aj0HS4-lTiudQ_9Uf3KhrZWNO8D8LRN1dgYTB4xV2b25JV_KUtvLupRPFa794I56DutSvlpWeu1bXhrtE1gHAmGqZaOXcKxeQ0u1iZnJvf-vv8wzqNETefqwKBchGMMkcT79JHb5whWs2pw9BQfg1z0rBro1SZsrPU3k0aS_Vuu4UqOPfLM6rBU3bgC3Zgo4PJFDoAGxA4So93CUo8ELIY8Ee710EeDGTlawK-8oXn10fwUkdmE9H7usx6jkRLn0SKlAFkrI0qxrabW9WzAiACScOYgqQmhrMkho9x6iPJdIEf7EeGtM6K1K6JwWmrJ_H96GfIy47peJLx2v4chE-c-7hVmNMMOYt1ufsaoVu1E